Canada July bankruptcies rise over year . Bankruptcies in Canada rose to 7 , 454 in July from 5 , 835 a year earlier , the Department of Consumer and Corporate Affairs said on Wednesday . The department said 1 , 076 businesses and 6 , 378 consumers went bankrupt in the month . In June , 7 , 268 bankruptcies were recorded . For the year to date , 54 , 281 bankruptcies have been registered ( 8 , 642 businesses and 45 , 639 consumers ) , up from 43 , 769 in the same period last year . - - Reuters Ottawa Bureau ( 613 ) 235 - 6745 
